data.description: Located in Rock Hill's Ellis Pond community is this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom two story home with tons to offer including a side-entry double garage, covered front porch, and fenced back yard! Inside are several desirable features; main floor primary suite, a formal living room and formal dining room, a loft area, and an upstairs bonus room perfect for an exercise room, media room, or office. Versatile space to fit all your needs with stylish touches throughout like barn doors! Bedrooms come with upgraded lighting, padded plush carpeting, and walk in closets. This house is more than meets the eye and one you don't want to miss! *Back on market - no fault to the sellers.* Sellers are very motivated and would prefer a quick closing if possible.
